==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bude light
<hw>Bude" light`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[From <ets>Bude</ets>, in
Cornwall, the residence of <person>Sir G. Gurney</person>, the
inventor.]</ety> <def>A light in which high illuminating power is
obtained by introducing a jet of oxygen gas or of common air into the
center of a flame fed with coal gas or with oil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Budge</ent>⟦br⟧
